{"type":"message","id":"90a33ae8","parentId":"aaa6da14","timestamp":"2026-03-26T07:50:28.840Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问两个执行任务是什么。从系统消息来看：\n\n1. `[2026-03-26 07:46:44 UTC] Exec failed (rapid-ba, signal SIGKILL)` - 这是一个执行任务失败了，被SIGKILL信号终止\n\n2. 发送者信息显示这是从 `openclaw-tui` (gateway-client) 发来的，标签是 \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\"\n\n这是在问之前我执行的那两个 exec 命令是做什么的：\n1. `df -h / | tail -1` - 检查磁盘空间\n2. `free -h` - 检查内存使用情况\n\n还有第三个命令 `openclaw gateway status` - 检查网关状态\n\n这些是我的心跳检查（HEARTBEAT.md）里定义的系统状态检查任务。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这两个是**心跳检查**任务：\n\n1. **`df -h / | tail -1`** → 检查磁盘空间使用情况\n   - 结果：225GB总容量，已用24G（11%）\n\n2. **`free -h`** → 检查内存使用情况\n   - 结果：总内存7GB，已用5.2GB，可用1.5GB\n\n另外还有一个 `openclaw gateway status` → 检查OpenClaw网关运行状态\n\n这些是按照 `HEARTBEAT.md` 里配置的每日检查任务执行的，用于监控系统健康状态。\n\n那个 **Exec failed (SIGKILL)** 是之前某个任务被系统终止了，和心跳检查无关。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-newapi","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":12778,"output":300,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13078,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774511417243,"responseId":"chatcmpl-99f66e77a6291181"}}
