{"type":"message","id":"50b4fa74","parentId":"a55bdd66","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:27:19.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway is running. Let me also quickly test the Telegram bot is reachable by hitting the Telegram API directly to see if the bot is working. Actually, first let me provide a summary to the user about what I've found so far, then suggest next steps.\n\nLooking at what we have:\n1. ✅ Gateway is running on port 18\n2. ✅ Telegram is configured and appears to be polling (last update ID shows activity)\n3. ✅ Both API endpoints tested and working\n4. The gateway status command is hanging, which might be a separate issue but not critical\n\nLet me summarize and suggest next steps.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n## 📋 任务执行结果\n\n### ✅ 1. 检查API配置\n\n| 配置项 | 状态 | 详情 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| **DeepSeek** | ✅ 已配置 | `api.deepseek.com/v1`, key: `sk-795c87...` |\n| **Claude/EPSQ** | ✅ 已配置 | `newapi.epsq.cn/v1`, key: `sk-GJRr6h...` |\n| **Telegram** | ✅ 已配置 | Bot: `8778664...`, 允许用户: `10` |\n\n### ⚠️ 2. 重启Telegram通道\n\nTelegram状态检查：\n- 最后收到更新: `421540511` (表示轮询在工作)\n- 网关运行正常: `curl http://127.0.0.1:18789/health` → `{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}`\n\n**问题**：`openclaw gateway status` 命令卡住，可能是Termux环境下的兼容性问题。\n\n是否需要我：\n1. 重启整个网关服务？\n2. 只重启Telegram插件？\n\n### ✅ 3. 网络监控\n\n之前的测试结果：\n| API | 状态 |\n|-----|------|\n| DeepSeek | ✅ 正常 |\n| Claude/EPSQ | ✅ 正常 |\n\n---\n\n请熊哥指示下一步～ 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-newapi-epsq-cn","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":19522,"output":408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19930,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774571230763,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7a626b9a2b35239cca6d94d8d5855843"}}
